{"tid":1078294,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返細個玩既pc game","createTime":"2019-03-26T07:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T20:43:33.000Z","uid":14902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2c9bed9418f0bb9a73ca61b28bbf22d5a23664","tid":1078294,"uid":14902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"其實我既印象唔係清楚 如果記錯唔好屌太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我玩緊時候應該係 05-06年左右<br />\n係日文game黎<br />\n淨係會控制一隻機械人（好似打怪過關咁樣）<br />\n機械人有得學唔同既技能,(我淨係得幾招: 撞擊,格林機關槍,類似等離子炮咁)<br />\n好似係有得連技咁...幾有打擊感<br />\n應該係2.5D <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上係我對隻game既印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4530941b24f1317cc6a01d46d1c754b6333607b5","tid":1078294,"uid":14902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9349660766e221bcdd225f1f6819629148f7dc7","tid":1078294,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"洛克人 Dash2?"},{"pid":"24c12658c4946a847e7521daaab9a819628c24b9","tid":1078294,"uid":14902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9349660766e221bcdd225f1f6819629148f7dc7","tid":1078294,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"洛克人 Dash2?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"應該唔係...我記得d 機械人係有小小gundam feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tw thanks"},{"pid":"03baced97532564339b7a7627491620f6cfd72a0","ti